    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/d25f53894b2b8c3cbeb596bb4b550c23.avif?t=1761905691\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><br>在炽热合金的世界中，机器统治着地球，活下来的少数人类也处在灭绝的边缘。在金属和电路组成的新统治者面前，人类失去了能源、地位和尊严。带上你最好的朋友和满满的子弹，射爆那堆废铜烂铁，解放人类同胞，体验子弹横飞的刺激和爽快吧！ <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/8d483f796a565bbc9378e4dd8e3a6fb8.poster.avif?t=1761905691\" width=610 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/8d483f796a565bbc9378e4dd8e3a6fb8.webm?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/8d483f796a565bbc9378e4dd8e3a6fb8.mp4?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/492c62c5be11aba74eea23de4ef6bc86.avif?t=1761905691\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><br>人工智能组成的机器人大军控制了地球，成了世界的主宰者。人类已是濒危物种，藏在阴暗的角落里躲避机器的猎杀。一个小的反抗组织得到情报，有机会摧毁AI的能量核心。但还没来得及动手，他们的基地就遭到了机器人的伏击。几个反抗军幸存了下来，决心执行毁掉能量核心的自杀任务。<br><br>你有两个角色可以选择，一个是莫拉，一名战斗力爆表的人类抵抗军战士，另一个是道尔，一名同样致命的反叛军机器人。<br><br>这次自杀任务必将会子弹横飞，造成伤亡无数，如疾风骤雨，让人眼花缭乱。拿上你强大的武器，把那些机器人变回炽热的废铁。杀出一条血路，你的自由就在前方！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/a0116e44320276f14d84b22d6db74f59.poster.avif?t=1761905691\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/a0116e44320276f14d84b22d6db74f59.webm?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/a0116e44320276f14d84b22d6db74f59.mp4?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/e45c02c32bb359fd629e641631bcd389.avif?t=1761905691\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><br>闯过5个充满末世风情的关卡，将成百上千的机器敌人射成渣渣。穿上重型铠甲、带起各种帅气的武器、骑上悬浮摩托，杀出一条血路，挑战一众的巨型机器人Boss。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/87a311e582693dd6b9f51f8a1c7016e7.poster.avif?t=1761905691\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/87a311e582693dd6b9f51f8a1c7016e7.webm?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/87a311e582693dd6b9f51f8a1c7016e7.mp4?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/f175ae63d104cb4cd6dfc51a2f7b9fa2.avif?t=1761905691\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><br>炽热合金具备经典横版射击动作游戏的诸多特点： <br>● 支持本地多人合作游玩<br>● 16 bit复古风格打造的末世环境<br>● 经典的快节奏横版动作射击体验<br>● 华丽刺激的Boss战和数量超多的小型Boss战<br>● 高还原度的复古街机体验<br>● 摩托车和喷气背包助阵<br>● 超带感的像素画风<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/0b7ca1dcb57deeec0324da4afda694dd.poster.avif?t=1761905691\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/0b7ca1dcb57deeec0324da4afda694dd.webm?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609110/extras/0b7ca1dcb57deeec0324da4afda694dd.mp4?t=1761905691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
